# Runtime installers are downloaded by the user (see Bundle.wxs comments)
# and embedded into the bundle at build time. Don't commit them — they're
# 25-60 MB and freely available from microsoft.com. The service bundle
# was on the base runtime (dotnet-runtime-*) up to 2026-05-12, then
# switched to the Desktop runtime (windowsdesktop-runtime-*) to share
# one installer with DraxClientSetup. Both patterns kept here so older
# branches still ignore correctly.
dotnet-runtime-*-win-x64.exe
dotnet-runtime-*-win-x86.exe
windowsdesktop-runtime-*-win-x64.exe
windowsdesktop-runtime-*-win-x86.exe
